     <p>In the above problem, the BSA of the patient was provided, but what if a calculation requires you to first calculate the BSA of a patient and then calculate the drug dose? 
     BSA of a patient can be estimated from their height and weight using either the <i>Nomogram</i> method or the <i>Mosteller</i> equation. 
     
